{"tid":677031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳寶珠嘆年青人唔夠敬老：因生活太幸福","createTime":"2018-05-25T00:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T09:35:15.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":317,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"024477ede3b7846a7bcf8dd8458d646f06ab089f","tid":677031,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T00:29:07.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】陳寶珠及梅雪詩（阿嗲）到長者中心出席記者會，宣佈將於8月底舉行《童心護老任白緣》籌款晚會，籌募院舍的翻新經費。會上有小演員在兩位粵劇名伶面前獻唱，二人大讚小朋友的造手及表情細緻，阿嗲笑指當年也不識驚，膽敢在師傅任劍輝及白雪仙面前表演。<br />\n<br />\n寶珠姐慨嘆時下年青人對父母及長輩的態度不及她們那一代好，皆因現在的生活太幸福，「以前有得去飲很開心，因為可以飲汽水，家里不捨得花錢買呢。」笑指她下月也有機會去飲汽水，皆因要出席薛家燕兒子的婚宴，寶珠姐即笑謂：「現在不能飲太多汽水啦，我本來11日要啟程到澳門準備演出，也延遲1日才出發，飲完才去。」她指「七公主」已約好要扮靚去飲，皆因眾人也是「大姨媽」，又笑問不知一對新人要否斟茶給她？<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0HfIMdB_IM9rAB7lEDZTHA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180524f200140.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F0HfIMdB_IM9rAB7lEDZTHA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180524f200140.jpg&h=b9525d31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%99%B3%E5%AF%B6%E7%8F%A0%E5%98%86%E5%B9%B4%E9%9D%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%94%94%E5%A4%A0%E6%95%AC%E8%80%81-%E5%9B%A0%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B8%E7%A6%8F-111800315.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E7%258F%25A0%25E5%2598%2586%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%259D%2592%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25A4%25A0%25E6%2595%25AC%25E8%2580%2581-%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25B9%25B8%25E7%25A6%258F-111800315.html&d=8P8rv8oVU7T5x%2FhCmoa3YS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=821c049e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%99%B3%E5%AF%B6%E7%8F%A0%E5%98%86%E5%B9%B4%E9%9D%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%94%94%E5%A4%A0%E6%95%AC%E8%80%81-%E5%9B%A0%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%